
<div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-light rounded-3">
  <div class="container-fluid py-5">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Fast Evaluation for Parkinsonism</h1>
    <img class="rounded float-end" style="width: 275px; max-width: 90%" src=<%=image_path("Parkinson-rafiki.png")%>>
    <p class="col-md-8 fs-4">
      Parkinsonism is a clinical syndrome including tremors, bradykinesia, rigidity, and postural instability. 
      Our tool provides a video-based platform to help users self-evaluate the possibility of Parkinsonism. <br>
      <br>
      Our 3 main features: <br>
      (1) Track over time. <br>
      (2) Compare between left and right side. <br>
      (3) Give a predicted-UPDRS score and quantitative parameters. <br>
      <b> Note: this tool is NOT a standard clinical evaluation tool but a preliminary tool for self-tracking. </b> <br>
      <br>
      <%= link_to("Start Now", dashboard_index_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg", data: {turbo: "false"}) %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

